div.div:
# create a new repo
mkdir "c:\OGS Projects"
cd "c:\OGS Projects"
git init
# link it to the production server repo
git remote add origin \\myserver\myrepopath
# use only folders path/sub1 and path/sub2 (e.g. this station)
git sparse-checkout set path/sub1 path/sub2
# for the first local repo:
git checkout -b main
# download files
git fetch --depth=1 origin maingit checkout main
# allow access
git config --global --add safe.directory "C:/OGS Projects"
